||241||
Na radhairc a chonaic mé ar Loch Súilí inniu:

                                                           Tusa ag breathnú ormsa?

                                                                    Tá tú agam!

                                                                 Tabhair dom é!

                                                                       Yum yum!

                                                                   Ní colm mise!

                                                                  Snámhaí Féileacáin?

                                                                   Scáth ar sciathán. 

                                                                 Cos-scamallach. 

                                                                     Am imeacht.

                                                       An bealach seo, le do thoil...

                                                                     Slán abhaile!




